headline: Amazon’s Potential US$50b OpenAI Deal And What It Means For Investors
summary: Amazon.com (NasdaqGS:AMZN) is reportedly in advanced talks to invest up to US$50b in OpenAI. The potential deal would be part of a wider US$100b funding round for OpenAI.
